summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6266 for the improvement of the alley in Block 3, Francies R. Day's La Grande Addition, as established by King County Court Cause No. 393405, being the alley between Whitman Ave. North and Woodland Park Ave. North from NOrth 39th Street to North 40th Street; and certain other alleys; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 91351, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
